data.name: ReadCase
data.value: select top(1) OFF_GENERATED_ID, NUMB from CKT_CASE where @offGeneratedId = OFF_GENERATED_ID

data.name: ReadCountyService
data.value: select top(1) SYSTEM_GENERATD_ID, OFF_GENERATED_ID from CKT_COUNTY_SERVICE where @offGeneratedId = OFF_GENERATED_ID

data.name: ReadOffice
data.value: select top(1) OFFICE_ID, OFF_OFFICE from CKT_OFFICE where OFFICE_ID = @officeId

data.name: ReadOfficeAssignmentPlan
data.value: select top(1) OFF_GENERATED_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, ASSIGNMENT_TYPE from CKT_OFCE_ASGMT_PLN where @offGeneratedId = OFF_GENERATED_ID

data.name: ReadOfficeCaseloadAssignment
data.value: select top(1) OFCE_CSLD_ASSGN_ID, OFF_GENERATED_ID from CKT_OFCE_CSLD_ASGT where @offGeneratedId = OFF_GENERATED_ID

data.name: ReadOfficeServiceProvider
data.value: select top(1) SPD_GENERATED_ID, OFF_GENERATED_ID, ROLE_CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE from CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR where @offGeneratedId = OFF_GENERATED_ID
